Mark Twain said “Get a bicycle. You will not regret it if you live.” Recycled brown paper is collected from a local packaging factory. This is then screen printed with the BICYCLES design.

Then it is fused to a special cotton to make it strong enough to stitch.

Once made up by our team of very skilled seamstresses the sleeve is sprayed with Nano Liquid Glass to be water resistant. ProjectZA.com to shop.
